WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:0
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:01:34.210 --> 00:01:36.580
Become My Servant

3
00:01:36.580 --> 00:01:38.850
What?! Hold on a second!

4
00:01:38.850 --> 00:01:43.120
That's what happened at the tea party-chocolat ?!

5
00:01:43.120 --> 00:01:45.440
I-It was the Straw Hats?!

6
00:01:45.440 --> 00:01:50.430
Yeah, it was a disaster!
The wedding and the wedding cake were both ruined!

7
00:01:50.430 --> 00:01:52.740
Our plan to assassinate the Vinsmokes failed!

8
00:01:52.740 --> 00:01:57.710
And on top of all that, Bege had been plotting
against us and was planning to kill Mama!

9
00:01:57.710 --> 00:02:03.540
That damn Bege... To think
I respected him for his abilities-noir !

10
00:02:03.540 --> 00:02:08.210
But we still don't know anything about the explosion.

11
00:02:04.100 --> 00:02:08.210
Eldest Daughter
of the Charlotte Family

12
00:02:10.670 --> 00:02:15.910
Those fools were on the rooftops with us,
so if they did it, they must've been suicidal.

13
00:02:15.910 --> 00:02:17.480
So that's unlikely.

14
00:02:17.480 --> 00:02:21.880
But at least we have solved one mystery-mour.

15
00:02:21.880 --> 00:02:23.700
During the tea party,

16
00:02:23.700 --> 00:02:28.020
all lines of communication
to the venue were jammed-bon !

17
00:02:28.020 --> 00:02:31.120
It was probably Bege and his allies.

18
00:02:31.120 --> 00:02:34.250
Was there something you needed to report?

19
00:02:34.250 --> 00:02:40.280
Well, the Sun Pirates, who had been
staying on the eastern coast–

20
00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:44.080
That's right! They ran out on us!

21
00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:45.220
Pekoms?!

22
00:02:45.220 --> 00:02:50.170
Those pirate fishmen
packed their bags and hit the road!

23
00:02:50.170 --> 00:02:54.220
I see... So that's why Jinbe did that.

24
00:02:56.190 --> 00:02:57.130
Jinbe...

25
00:02:58.140 --> 00:03:02.870
left the Big Mom Pirates,
and joined forces with the Straw Hat crew.

26
00:03:03.810 --> 00:03:07.230
What?! Jinbe left?!

27
00:03:07.230 --> 00:03:10.240
Yeah...
and now his actions make sense.

28
00:03:11.950 --> 00:03:14.260
He knew that Mama
would take revenge on his friends.

29
00:03:14.260 --> 00:03:17.070
So in order to tell his friends
and give them time to flee,

30
00:03:17.070 --> 00:03:20.040
Jinbe took back his previous request to leave.

31
00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:23.950
That sounds like Jinbe.
A very thorough strategy, indeed.

32
00:03:23.950 --> 00:03:25.580
Katakuri!

33
00:03:25.580 --> 00:03:29.250
We've already sent troops
after Straw Hat and Bege.

34
00:03:30.100 --> 00:03:31.250
All right.

35
00:03:31.250 --> 00:03:34.640
And another group is laying siege to Germa.

36
00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:38.060
Good... Brûlée, come with me!

37
00:03:38.060 --> 00:03:43.680
Of course, Brother!
Are you going to take out Straw Hat and the others?

38
00:03:43.680 --> 00:03:45.520
I wanna make them pay!

39
00:03:45.520 --> 00:03:49.610
They abused me over and over

40
00:03:49.610 --> 00:03:52.900
and made me help them try to kill Mama!

41
00:03:53.610 --> 00:03:55.780
That's my plan...

42
00:03:55.780 --> 00:03:58.290
I'm gonna cut off Straw Hat's head!

43
00:03:59.110 --> 00:04:03.940
I've decided that it's important
to get rid of him

44
00:04:03.940 --> 00:04:06.750
before he becomes a true threat
to Mama later down the line.

45
00:04:23.810 --> 00:04:26.430
Everyone! Escape from the city!

46
00:04:26.430 --> 00:04:27.730
Smoothie!

47
00:04:28.390 --> 00:04:30.330
Run as far as you can!

48
00:04:34.410 --> 00:04:35.770
At a time like this?!

49
00:04:35.770 --> 00:04:38.330
What's the matter, Smoothie?!

50
00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:42.010
Everybody! Run!

51
00:04:50.540 --> 00:04:54.380
Don't tell me... it's happening now ?!

52
00:04:54.520 --> 00:04:58.610
Germa Kingdom

53
00:04:58.610 --> 00:05:01.890
I can't reach
Generalissimo Judge or Prince Ichiji!

54
00:05:01.890 --> 00:05:04.030
What happened?

55
00:05:05.520 --> 00:05:06.390
What's that?!

56
00:05:12.520 --> 00:05:14.490
The Big Mom Pirates?!

57
00:05:22.880 --> 00:05:26.880
Where is the... wedding cake?!

58
00:05:41.820 --> 00:05:44.320
The queen's ravenous rampage!

59
00:05:44.320 --> 00:05:48.650
She's having another attack so soon?!

60
00:05:51.760 --> 00:05:56.580
She remembered that the wedding cake was destroyed
and that she didn't get to eat it!

61
00:06:02.960 --> 00:06:05.590
What's that in Mama's hand?!

62
00:06:10.590 --> 00:06:13.180
It's too late.

63
00:06:20.350 --> 00:06:21.790
Oh, no!

64
00:06:30.190 --> 00:06:31.880
Big Brother Opera!

65
00:06:31.880 --> 00:06:34.440
Hey! Wake up!

66
00:06:34.440 --> 00:06:36.300
Don't tell me she took your lifespan!

67
00:06:36.300 --> 00:06:37.790
Big Brother!

68
00:06:38.820 --> 00:06:43.290
Brother Opera stood in Mama's way
to stop her!

69
00:06:44.460 --> 00:06:47.920
Everyone stay away from Mama!

70
00:06:57.730 --> 00:07:00.940
We have to do something...

71
00:07:00.940 --> 00:07:02.600
Where is it?!

72
00:07:03.540 --> 00:07:07.280
The wedding cake?!

73
00:07:19.650 --> 00:07:22.710
Everyone, hurry up!
They're going to catch up to us!

74
00:07:23.790 --> 00:07:24.960
Nami!

75
00:07:24.960 --> 00:07:29.270
You're riding on Jinbe's shoulders!
Don't boss us around!

76
00:07:29.270 --> 00:07:31.130
It's okay!

77
00:07:31.130 --> 00:07:33.850
Because Nami-san is so cute!

78
00:07:33.850 --> 00:07:36.090
So cute and delicate...

79
00:07:38.350 --> 00:07:43.410
The Big Mom Pirates will definitel
send forces after us! We must hurry!

80
00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:45.620
You can count on me!

81
00:07:45.620 --> 00:07:51.420
Going through this area and then through the Seducing
Woods is the fastest way back to the Sunny !

82
00:07:57.430 --> 00:07:58.910
You all know what to do!

83
00:07:58.910 --> 00:08:03.970
The only way to stop Mama's ravenous rampge...
is to give her the food she craves!

84
00:08:07.380 --> 00:08:11.110
The food we need... is the wedding cake!

85
00:08:11.110 --> 00:08:16.590
Where is the head chef?!
He's the only person capable of remaking that cake!

86
00:08:16.590 --> 00:08:19.390
W-Well... Head Chef Streusen...

87
00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:22.390
saved everyone's life, but...

88
00:08:23.890 --> 00:08:27.310
his own landing was catastrophic!

89
00:08:32.140 --> 00:08:35.610
He needs several days to recover!

90
00:08:38.990 --> 00:08:42.960
If this continues,
Sweet City will be destroyed!

91
00:08:42.960 --> 00:08:46.410
How are we going to stop Mama?!

92
00:08:49.290 --> 00:08:52.870
We can't let her rampage here in the capital!

93
00:09:02.660 --> 00:09:05.340
Where is it?!

94
00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.780
Does he...

95
00:09:10.780 --> 00:09:12.760
I guess he's got an idea!

96
00:09:12.760 --> 00:09:15.600
That's the Great Perospero for you!

97
00:09:17.340 --> 00:09:20.810
Mama! The wedding cake...

98
00:09:20.810 --> 00:09:23.430
isn't gone!

99
00:09:26.980 --> 00:09:30.940
There was a backup cake, Mama!

100
00:09:32.010 --> 00:09:33.510
Brother Peros!

101
00:09:33.510 --> 00:09:35.600
No! What are you saying?!

102
00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:41.370
I-It was made out of
carefully selected ingredients...

103
00:09:41.370 --> 00:09:44.950
and it's delicious enough
to melt in your mouth!

104
00:09:44.950 --> 00:09:48.830
It's the perfect wedding cake!

105
00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:52.400
Mama, we'd love for you to have it,

106
00:09:52.400 --> 00:09:56.530
but the Straw Hats stole it and ran!

107
00:09:56.530 --> 00:10:01.700
Now they're heading to the southwest beach
in an attempt to escape!

108
00:10:03.430 --> 00:10:05.320
Wedding...

109
00:10:05.900 --> 00:10:08.090
cake...

110
00:10:08.090 --> 00:10:12.440
That's right! They've got it, lick!

111
00:10:13.340 --> 00:10:15.910
She can still listen to some reason.

112
00:10:15.910 --> 00:10:20.620
If she goes after Straw Hat,
that'll take out two birds with one stone.

113
00:10:24.640 --> 00:10:26.920
Can he convince her?

114
00:10:40.340 --> 00:10:43.510
If you're lying to me

115
00:10:43.510 --> 00:10:48.060
you'll pay with your lifespan!

116
00:10:53.190 --> 00:10:54.260
Zeus!

117
00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:56.490
Yes, Mama?

118
00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:11.540
Wedding cake!

119
00:11:22.150 --> 00:11:24.070
I'm screwed!

120
00:11:24.070 --> 00:11:29.260
Even if Mama catches the Straw Hats, they don't actually have a cake!

121
00:11:29.260 --> 00:11:32.980
What should I do?!

122
00:11:30.380 --> 00:11:32.980
That seemed like a good plan, but...

123
00:11:36.770 --> 00:11:40.380
When Mama comes back,
I'll be killed!

124
00:11:40.730 --> 00:11:42.590
But you bought us some time!

125
00:11:42.590 --> 00:11:46.250
We've got to bake a cake now.
Otherwise, this island is finished!

126
00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:51.840
No, it's impossible...
Think about it, Smoothie.

127
00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:58.430
How many days do you think it took
Head Chef Streusen to make that cake?

128
00:11:59.090 --> 00:12:04.680
The rare ingredients that we plundered
from other countries are gone.

129
00:12:05.050 --> 00:12:10.650
And the one man who can bake it is unconscious!
There will be no cake!

130
00:12:12.150 --> 00:12:18.610
To make matters worse...
Mama didn't even get to taste the first cake at all...

131
00:12:18.610 --> 00:12:20.700
So this time, we'll have to provide...

132
00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:28.830
...a cake that Mama's imagination has run wild with.
One that she's never tasted before!

133
00:12:28.830 --> 00:12:33.920
Who in the world can make such a thing?!

134
00:12:34.460 --> 00:12:36.380
This is bad.

135
00:12:36.380 --> 00:12:38.510
At best, she'll just destroy the island...

136
00:12:38.510 --> 00:12:41.920
But what happens beyond that...
is unknown.

137
00:12:55.730 --> 00:12:58.640
Do you want me to help you?!

138
00:13:05.820 --> 00:13:07.280
Pudding!

139
00:13:07.280 --> 00:13:09.100
Oh, Madam Pudding!

140
00:13:09.100 --> 00:13:10.410
Madam Pudding!

141
00:13:10.410 --> 00:13:14.990
The first wedding cake
was a chocolate chiffon cake!

142
00:13:14.990 --> 00:13:19.920
When it comes to chocolate,
I'm every bit as good as the head chef!

143
00:13:19.920 --> 00:13:24.840
And Sister Chiffon is an expert
at making chiffon cakes!

144
00:13:24.840 --> 00:13:28.880
The two of us together can make that cake!

145
00:13:28.880 --> 00:13:30.980
Is that true, Pudding?!

146
00:13:30.980 --> 00:13:35.470
But Chiffon is Bege's wife,
and he's our enemy now!

147
00:13:37.330 --> 00:13:39.630
I'll force her to do it.

148
00:13:39.630 --> 00:13:41.390
There's the evil Pudding!

149
00:13:41.390 --> 00:13:44.900
What?! Madam Pudding is acting like a thug!

150
00:13:46.490 --> 00:13:49.410
The truth is, the ingredients for the cake

151
00:13:49.410 --> 00:13:53.270
were stored in Chocolat Town, on Cacao Island,

152
00:13:53.270 --> 00:13:54.980
the gateway of our territory.

153
00:13:55.780 --> 00:13:59.120
So that's where backup ingredients should be.

154
00:14:00.450 --> 00:14:01.630
Brother Peros!

155
00:14:01.630 --> 00:14:05.460
Once Mama eliminates the Straw Hats,
guide her to Chocolat Town!

156
00:14:06.250 --> 00:14:08.800
I'll end this problem!

157
00:14:09.460 --> 00:14:12.720
Is this true?!
You're so helpful, Pudding!

158
00:14:14.570 --> 00:14:17.720
Sanji humiliated me!

159
00:14:17.720 --> 00:14:20.640
What a beautiful eye!

160
00:14:21.320 --> 00:14:23.650
If Mama can wipe them out...

161
00:14:24.500 --> 00:14:27.270
I have to give her a reward.

162
00:14:32.110 --> 00:14:33.610
Just you wait,

163
00:14:33.610 --> 00:14:35.040
Sanji!

164
00:14:37.400 --> 00:14:38.300
What's wrong?

165
00:14:38.300 --> 00:14:41.260
My heart just thumped...

166
00:14:41.260 --> 00:14:44.020
I guess some cutie
is talking about me like always.

167
00:14:44.020 --> 00:14:46.210
I see the Seducing Woods!

168
00:14:46.740 --> 00:14:51.080
Are we gonna go into that forest again?!
I hope we'll be okay.

169
00:14:51.960 --> 00:14:53.470
Hey, what's that?

170
00:14:55.130 --> 00:14:58.420
No, stop, Kin-chan !

171
00:14:58.430 --> 00:15:00.900
Are you okay, Kin-chan ?

172
00:15:00.900 --> 00:15:05.720
Ow, ow, ow!
The seam hurts, Lady Tree...

173
00:15:05.720 --> 00:15:11.480
I'm sorry... But they'll stick together soon.
Just like us!

174
00:15:11.480 --> 00:15:15.650
Ow, ow, ow! Take it easy.

175
00:15:20.450 --> 00:15:22.580
What? No! How?!

176
00:15:23.490 --> 00:15:25.240
Hey!

177
00:15:26.410 --> 00:15:28.120
Hey!

178
00:15:28.870 --> 00:15:32.220
You're alive, Kingbaum!

179
00:15:33.750 --> 00:15:35.850
It's good to see you again!

180
00:15:35.850 --> 00:15:37.550
Tree!

181
00:15:42.050 --> 00:15:43.810
G... G...

182
00:15:44.680 --> 00:15:47.400
Go away!

183
00:15:47.400 --> 00:15:50.800
I'll make you pay, you bastards!

184
00:15:50.800 --> 00:15:52.100
Kin-chan !

185
00:15:52.100 --> 00:15:54.110
Lady Tree!

186
00:15:57.160 --> 00:15:59.370
Don't look back! Go straight!

187
00:15:59.810 --> 00:16:01.910
Dammit!

188
00:16:01.910 --> 00:16:06.990
Oh? Nami, I thought
they took Lola's vivre card.

189
00:16:06.990 --> 00:16:09.760
Yes, they did.
But I cut it in two!

190
00:16:09.760 --> 00:16:11.040
That's smart!

191
00:16:11.040 --> 00:16:13.270
This is fast!

192
00:16:13.270 --> 00:16:17.120
Since he's the master of the Seducing Woods,
he can take us straight through it.

193
00:16:17.120 --> 00:16:20.570
All right!
Keep going to the Sunny at full speed!

194
00:16:20.570 --> 00:16:21.880
Go!

195
00:16:21.880 --> 00:16:27.250
You guys are like the plague!
Leave this country already!

196
00:16:27.250 --> 00:16:28.710
Did you say something?

197
00:16:29.680 --> 00:16:32.430
Do as Nami-san says!

198
00:16:38.820 --> 00:16:43.830
Our targets are right there!
Take them down!

199
00:16:43.830 --> 00:16:47.040
Yeah!

200
00:16:48.200 --> 00:16:50.480
Look, our enemies are behind us!

201
00:16:51.640 --> 00:16:52.960
Charge!

202
00:16:52.960 --> 00:16:55.520
Yeah!

203
00:16:56.120 --> 00:16:57.860
Go faster, Kingbaum!

204
00:16:57.860 --> 00:16:59.800
I'm going as fast as I can!

205
00:16:59.800 --> 00:17:02.520
If you get caught, I'll rip that seam!

206
00:17:02.520 --> 00:17:03.930
You're terrible!

207
00:17:08.470 --> 00:17:10.310
Something passed over our heads!

208
00:17:13.480 --> 00:17:14.400
That voice...

209
00:17:14.400 --> 00:17:15.440
No way!

210
00:17:18.810 --> 00:17:20.500
What?!

211
00:17:20.500 --> 00:17:27.700
Wedding cake!

212
00:17:28.490 --> 00:17:31.330
Big Mom!

213
00:17:35.170 --> 00:17:37.760
Give it to me!

214
00:17:38.910 --> 00:17:43.700
Meanwhile, near the Juice River
in Sweet City...

215
00:17:45.660 --> 00:17:50.040
Oh, there it is! The Juice River!

216
00:17:50.040 --> 00:17:53.460
The Shark Submerge is anchored there!

217
00:17:54.050 --> 00:17:55.840
So that's the river...

218
00:17:58.890 --> 00:18:00.610
What?!

219
00:18:00.610 --> 00:18:03.640
This river is filled with heavy cream!

220
00:18:03.640 --> 00:18:06.390
Oh, it smells good!

221
00:18:08.600 --> 00:18:12.380
It looks delicious! I'm gonna eat it!

222
00:18:13.910 --> 00:18:15.570
It's so sweet!

223
00:18:15.570 --> 00:18:21.950
I can't believe the debris from
the crumbled Whole Cake Chateau flew this far...

224
00:18:23.120 --> 00:18:25.770
Mmm! Mmm! It's so good!

225
00:18:25.780 --> 00:18:29.380
Now, what should we do...

226
00:18:29.380 --> 00:18:30.830
I mean, Chopper-san !

227
00:18:35.170 --> 00:18:38.090
Yum!

228
00:18:45.480 --> 00:18:48.280
Big Mom is getting closer!

229
00:18:49.260 --> 00:18:51.010
Why is Mama at the front line?

230
00:18:51.010 --> 00:18:53.500
But look at her...
Something's wrong with Mama!

231
00:18:53.920 --> 00:18:56.300
Don't tell me she's on a ravenous rampage!

232
00:18:56.300 --> 00:19:00.140
Wedding cake!

233
00:19:00.140 --> 00:19:02.600
Shake her off, Kingbaum!

234
00:19:02.600 --> 00:19:04.360
That's impossible!

235
00:19:08.080 --> 00:19:12.230
Taste the Spear of Elbaf...

236
00:19:12.230 --> 00:19:13.520
Elbaf?!

237
00:19:17.230 --> 00:19:19.140
Something's coming!

238
00:19:31.300 --> 00:19:33.400
Hegemony!

239
00:20:20.360 --> 00:20:23.250
Wedding...

240
00:20:23.590 --> 00:20:25.880
cake!

241
00:20:25.900 --> 00:20:29.930
That looked like the attack those giants used!

242
00:20:29.930 --> 00:20:32.220
Warrior's Might!

243
00:20:36.850 --> 00:20:38.020
Why's that?

244
00:20:38.890 --> 00:20:40.810
Kingbaum!

245
00:20:45.190 --> 00:20:49.990
Mama! Forgive me!
They're forcing me to do this!

246
00:20:52.280 --> 00:20:56.010
Oh, no! She's gonna attack again!
Let's get down there and fight!

247
00:20:56.010 --> 00:21:00.630
Kingbaum! Who was the girl you were with earlier?
Was she your girlfriend?

248
00:21:02.420 --> 00:21:05.530
No, stop, Kin-chan!

249
00:21:05.530 --> 00:21:08.090
Are you okay, Kin-chan?

250
00:21:08.090 --> 00:21:09.700
Kin-chan!

251
00:21:09.700 --> 00:21:11.640
Lady Tree!

252
00:21:12.130 --> 00:21:15.030
Sh-She's my fiancée.

253
00:21:15.030 --> 00:21:17.850
Wow! Your fiancée?!

254
00:21:18.900 --> 00:21:23.150
That's right!
We made a promise to be together forever!

255
00:21:23.160 --> 00:21:25.150
In that case...

256
00:21:25.150 --> 00:21:27.820
you must survive!

257
00:21:30.440 --> 00:21:33.100
Survive for her sake!

258
00:21:33.100 --> 00:21:35.450
So you can see her again!

259
00:21:44.210 --> 00:21:48.070
You're right!
I can't just give up now!

260
00:21:48.070 --> 00:21:50.250
Run, Kingbaum!

261
00:21:50.250 --> 00:21:54.540
You've got a whole life ahead of you with her!

262
00:21:54.540 --> 00:21:58.260
A life of love is waiting for you!

263
00:21:59.470 --> 00:22:01.930
Lady Tree!

264
00:22:02.730 --> 00:22:04.020
Yes!

265
00:22:05.020 --> 00:22:06.700
She's like a devil...

266
00:22:06.700 --> 00:22:08.340
That's our Nami!

267
00:22:08.340 --> 00:22:11.210
Give me my cake!

268
00:22:11.210 --> 00:22:12.970
Okay, it's my turn!

269
00:22:12.970 --> 00:22:16.080
Wait, Luffy! I have a plan!

270
00:22:16.080 --> 00:22:18.310
Wedding...

271
00:22:18.310 --> 00:22:19.910
What's the plan?!

272
00:22:22.120 --> 00:22:23.850
...cake!

273
00:22:23.850 --> 00:22:25.620
Black Ball!

274
00:22:30.840 --> 00:22:33.490
Thunder attracts thunder.

275
00:22:33.490 --> 00:22:35.180
Hegemony!

276
00:22:41.310 --> 00:22:42.330
That's it!

277
00:22:42.330 --> 00:22:44.000
He ate them!

278
00:22:44.000 --> 00:22:47.230
It's delicious! It's delicious! So delicious!

279
00:22:49.650 --> 00:22:51.400
Oh! Mama!

280
00:22:52.610 --> 00:22:55.030
Oh, wait!

281
00:22:55.040 --> 00:22:57.660
What are you doing, Zeus?!

282
00:22:58.110 --> 00:23:00.600
Oh no, he's distracted big time...

283
00:23:00.600 --> 00:23:04.520
They're running into the Seducing Woods!

284
00:23:04.520 --> 00:23:07.960
Wedding cake!

285
00:23:07.960 --> 00:23:11.670
Once we're in the woods,
we'll have the upper hand!

286
00:23:13.800 --> 00:23:16.680
Because Kingbaum is...

287
00:23:17.430 --> 00:23:19.640
the master of those woods!

288
00:23:19.640 --> 00:23:21.620
It's Master Kingbaum!

289
00:23:21.620 --> 00:23:24.750
Master Kingbaum is coming!

290
00:23:24.750 --> 00:23:27.110
Get out of my way!

291
00:23:32.900 --> 00:23:34.450
Awesome!

292
00:23:34.450 --> 00:23:35.600
Oh, my...

293
00:23:35.600 --> 00:23:37.400
You sure are something, big tree.

294
00:23:38.320 --> 00:23:40.410
Move! Move! Move!

295
00:23:49.340 --> 00:23:52.440
Oh, look! There's the Sunny !

296
00:23:52.440 --> 00:23:53.000
What?

297
00:23:53.000 --> 00:23:55.650
It's a straight shot to the coast!

298
00:23:55.650 --> 00:23:58.590
That was an amazing plan, Nami!

299
00:23:58.590 --> 00:24:01.640
That's our Nami-swan !

300
00:24:05.800 --> 00:24:09.610
As long as Big Mom doesn't get back on Zeus,
we can outrun them!

301
00:24:09.610 --> 00:24:11.240
His name is Zeus?

302
00:24:11.240 --> 00:24:15.240
Yes. That cloud is part of Mama's soul...

303
00:24:15.240 --> 00:24:16.910
Yeah, I'm Zeus.

304
00:24:16.910 --> 00:24:18.460
Master Zeus!

305
00:24:18.460 --> 00:24:19.400
Zeus!

306
00:24:19.400 --> 00:24:20.040
He's here!

307
00:24:20.040 --> 00:24:22.340
Be careful! He's powerful!

308
00:24:22.340 --> 00:24:27.450
Hey, hey, those small lightning clouds!
Can I have some more?

309
00:24:28.150 --> 00:24:29.280
What?

310
00:24:30.490 --> 00:24:33.350
My Black Ball? Did you enjoy them?

311
00:24:33.350 --> 00:24:38.710
I've never tasted such rich clouds before! And they weren't hard to eat at all!

312
00:24:38.710 --> 00:24:40.810
Hey, do you have more?

313
00:24:40.810 --> 00:24:43.590
Oh, they taste good?

314
00:24:48.970 --> 00:24:50.950
It's fluffy!

315
00:24:50.950 --> 00:24:54.280
Give me, give me, more, more!

316
00:24:54.280 --> 00:24:57.350
Hey, cloud!
Forget about that and give us a ride instead!

317
00:24:57.350 --> 00:25:03.000
No can do. Only Mama can ride me,
because she gave me her soul.

318
00:25:03.000 --> 00:25:05.460
Oh, so you're just a boring cloud?

319
00:25:05.460 --> 00:25:07.530
So boring...

320
00:25:07.530 --> 00:25:10.070
Zeus... in that case...

321
00:25:11.950 --> 00:25:14.550
will you be my servant?

322
00:25:14.550 --> 00:25:15.640
Huh?

323
00:25:15.640 --> 00:25:17.390
I will!

324
00:25:17.390 --> 00:25:19.630
She wasn't asking you...

325
00:25:19.630 --> 00:25:23.230
Then you can have Black Balls to eat
every single day!

326
00:25:23.230 --> 00:25:27.730
What? Really?!
What should I do?! What should I do?!

327
00:25:27.730 --> 00:25:30.370
So you don't have any loyalty to your boss, then?

328
00:25:31.340 --> 00:25:36.290
I noticed earlier that you're able
to completely cover the sky!

329
00:25:36.290 --> 00:25:38.660
That was so cool!

330
00:25:38.660 --> 00:25:40.800
Oh, you think so?

331
00:25:40.800 --> 00:25:44.100
No one's ever complimented me like that!

332
00:26:08.140 --> 00:26:10.350
M-Mama...

333
00:26:10.930 --> 00:26:12.480
Mama!

334
00:26:13.100 --> 00:26:15.900
Seducing Woods!

335
00:26:16.940 --> 00:26:19.440
Stop them!

336
00:26:30.370 --> 00:26:33.130
Oh, no! Mama's angry!

337
00:26:37.210 --> 00:26:39.670
They're back to being annoying again!

338
00:26:40.800 --> 00:26:43.680
Why can't we just smash them
and keep moving forward?

339
00:26:43.700 --> 00:26:45.210
That won't work!

340
00:26:45.210 --> 00:26:50.120
During your rampage, you'll just lose
all sense of direction in these woods...

341
00:26:50.120 --> 00:26:54.570
That's right.
These woods toy with a person's mind!

342
00:27:01.860 --> 00:27:05.540
We cannot disobey an order from the queen!

343
00:27:11.700 --> 00:27:12.880
But...!

344
00:27:15.370 --> 00:27:17.440
Lady Tree!

345
00:27:17.440 --> 00:27:19.020
Wait!

346
00:27:19.020 --> 00:27:23.060
Run as fast as you can,
for the sake of love and the future!

347
00:27:25.340 --> 00:27:27.490
Mama gave us an order! Stop them!

348
00:27:27.490 --> 00:27:29.360
Get out of my way!

349
00:27:29.360 --> 00:27:32.240
I'm not dying here!

350
00:27:32.240 --> 00:27:35.190
Why are you doing this, Master Kingbaum?!

351
00:27:38.140 --> 00:27:40.910
You can do it, Kingbaum!

352
00:27:44.530 --> 00:27:46.400
Hang on tight!

353
00:27:46.400 --> 00:27:47.090
Okay.

354
00:27:47.090 --> 00:27:49.380
Tree! Keep moving!

355
00:27:50.620 --> 00:27:52.960
Gum-Gum...

356
00:27:52.960 --> 00:27:55.880
Gatling!

357
00:28:18.030 --> 00:28:20.570
Oh, that's convenient.

358
00:28:24.330 --> 00:28:26.630
Ouch, it's getting hot. What is that?

359
00:28:26.640 --> 00:28:28.120
That's...

360
00:28:39.510 --> 00:28:42.030
It's Master Prometheus!

361
00:28:42.030 --> 00:28:44.280
He's angry!

362
00:28:44.280 --> 00:28:48.230
Hey, Kingbaum.

363
00:28:50.560 --> 00:28:53.490
You betrayed Mama...

364
00:28:54.900 --> 00:28:57.880
M-Master Prometheus!

365
00:28:57.880 --> 00:28:59.530
It's hot!

366
00:29:00.000 --> 00:29:02.870
He's coming this way!

367
00:29:02.870 --> 00:29:04.600
Is he trying to crush us?

368
00:29:04.600 --> 00:29:06.590
Kingbaum, get away!

369
00:29:13.880 --> 00:29:18.600
Kingbaum, run!
Your fiancée is waiting for you, right?!

370
00:29:24.360 --> 00:29:25.960
He can't move! Let's get off!

371
00:29:39.340 --> 00:29:40.480
Run!

372
00:29:40.480 --> 00:29:41.820
Nami! This way!

373
00:29:41.820 --> 00:29:42.940
Nami-san!

374
00:29:42.940 --> 00:29:44.820
You will get hurt, too!

375
00:29:44.820 --> 00:29:46.350
Nami!

376
00:30:01.450 --> 00:30:02.930
Tree!

377
00:30:05.040 --> 00:30:06.750
Kingbaum...

378
00:30:07.840 --> 00:30:08.930
Nami-san !

379
00:30:22.300 --> 00:30:27.600
Wedding cake!

380
00:30:31.770 --> 00:30:32.910
What about Bege?

381
00:30:32.910 --> 00:30:34.920
We'll catch up to him soon!

382
00:30:34.920 --> 00:30:37.860
There's a fire in the Seducing Woods...

383
00:30:36.440 --> 00:30:39.960
The Capital (Sweet City)

384
00:30:37.860 --> 00:30:39.950
I think Mama is fighting.

385
00:30:40.900 --> 00:30:44.010
This is the Mirro-world. Mont d'Or!

386
00:30:44.010 --> 00:30:49.070
We have 10,000 soldiers
who are waiting to be sent wherever you command!

387
00:30:44.080 --> 00:30:49.330
Mirro-world

388
00:30:51.920 --> 00:30:54.880
Got it. We'll be in touch.

389
00:30:54.880 --> 00:30:58.700
Candy! Biscuits! Nuts!

390
00:30:58.700 --> 00:31:03.970
Those island battleships should watch the southwest
coast where the Straw Hats' ship is anchored.

391
00:31:03.970 --> 00:31:06.360
Do not let them set sail!

392
00:31:06.360 --> 00:31:07.410
Yes, sir!

393
00:31:07.410 --> 00:31:11.650
You guys will be the first line of security...

394
00:31:11.650 --> 00:31:16.840
After that, I want the tarte ships
from Flavor Island and Liqueur Island...

395
00:31:16.840 --> 00:31:20.530
to be on standby, and ready to move.

396
00:31:20.530 --> 00:31:24.050
Wait until you hear the warning signal
from the territorial sea slugs.

397
00:31:24.050 --> 00:31:25.240
Roger.

398
00:31:27.820 --> 00:31:33.500
They won't be able to escape from our
territorial sea slug security network.

399
00:31:34.120 --> 00:31:38.130
The Sunny, Southwest Coast

400
00:31:38.130 --> 00:31:40.110
The woods sure are noisy...

401
00:31:40.110 --> 00:31:41.830
It makes sense...

402
00:31:43.380 --> 00:31:49.970
Mama's chasing them herself.
They have no chance of making it here.

403
00:31:49.970 --> 00:31:51.660
Indeed.

404
00:31:51.660 --> 00:31:55.560
In that case...
why are we waiting for them here?

405
00:31:56.390 --> 00:31:58.730
Just in case.

406
00:32:04.400 --> 00:32:07.380
The tarte tanks are chasing us.

407
00:32:07.380 --> 00:32:08.740
Fire!

408
00:32:11.820 --> 00:32:15.790
We're almost to the coast!
They won't catch up.

409
00:32:17.170 --> 00:32:18.760
Brother Bege!

410
00:32:18.760 --> 00:32:20.860
Wow! You scared me!

411
00:32:22.000 --> 00:32:27.110
Madam Pu– I mean, Pudding!
I won't show mercy, even if you are just a little girl!

412
00:32:27.110 --> 00:32:31.600
I need to talk to Sister Chiffon!
Bring her out, right now!

413
00:32:33.550 --> 00:32:35.730
Sister Chiffon! Where are you?

414
00:32:38.350 --> 00:32:40.540
Pudding! Why are you here?!

415
00:32:40.540 --> 00:32:41.730
Sister!

416
00:32:41.730 --> 00:32:44.940
I need your help!

417
00:32:44.940 --> 00:32:48.280
Mama's on one of her ravenous rampages!

418
00:32:48.280 --> 00:32:51.610
She's craving a wedding cake!

419
00:32:52.280 --> 00:32:54.470
A ravenous rampage?!

420
00:32:54.470 --> 00:32:59.240
Yes, and the wedding cake she wants
is a chocolate chiffon cake!

421
00:32:59.240 --> 00:33:01.880
That should be enough information for you.

422
00:33:03.790 --> 00:33:07.070
So you need my chiffon cake.

423
00:33:07.070 --> 00:33:13.460
Yes. If we combine my chocolate
and your chiffon cake,

424
00:33:13.460 --> 00:33:17.300
we can make a wedding cake
that will satisfy Mama!

425
00:33:17.300 --> 00:33:21.730
If we feed it to her,
we can stop her rampage!

426
00:33:28.900 --> 00:33:30.730
I'm sorry, Pudding...

427
00:33:30.730 --> 00:33:34.400
Just like Lola, I'm leaving this place.

428
00:33:34.400 --> 00:33:38.470
I no longer care what happens
to Mama or to this country!

429
00:33:38.470 --> 00:33:41.560
Yeah! So just go away, Pudding!

430
00:33:41.560 --> 00:33:43.000
That's not it...

431
00:33:50.090 --> 00:33:52.960
The real reason I'm doing this...

432
00:33:52.960 --> 00:33:55.770
isn't for Mama... or for this country!

433
00:33:55.770 --> 00:33:56.680
Hm?

434
00:34:00.750 --> 00:34:04.040
I need to stop Mama as soon as possible...

435
00:34:06.000 --> 00:34:07.590
Otherwise, he...

436
00:34:07.590 --> 00:34:11.380
and his friends will be killed!
